  "answer": "C)  lymphoma, thus needle biopsy is needed if confirmed ==> excisional\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_176.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_177.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_178.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_179.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_180.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_181.jpeg)\n\n\n\n![Image](/images/review_bank/467344482-General-Surgery-MCQ-Saudi_182.jpeg)",
